p: M.B. and S.L.B. conceived the project; all authors contributed to study design. P.C.K., M.B., and S.L.B. collected specimens. P.C.K. and M.B. performed dissections. P.C.K. and D.D.C. performed chemical analyses. P.C.K. and M.B. analyzed the data. All authors contributed to the preparation of the manuscript.
